features.text:
"The Blitnauts" is a limited run engagement celebrating four months of the Blitnauts expansions from NFT project Blitmap. 

On December 30th, 2021 a snapshot will be taken of all Blitmap pieces that have been 'attuned' in the process of generating a Blitnaut. Those Blitmap holders will later receive an airdrop for their attunement.

This show examines the emergent design decisions made by the community based on Blitmap color palettes, observed for the first time in a curated manner.

For more information regarding the Blitmap universe, visit blitmap.com
